# Dellite contract

Source of truth: root `AGENTS.md`. Wiki index for agents: `.cursor/docs/WIKI_MAP.md`.

## Non-negotiables

- Shared fundamentals → `packages/app-core`. No duplicate primitives across apps.
- Types only in `src/types/*` — never in screens, components, hooks, contexts, navigation.
- Thin `src/contexts/*`; logic in `src/hooks/use*Controller.ts`. Screens use context hooks only.
- No hardcoded UI copy or colors — use `appText.ts` and theme tokens.
- User-facing dates — use `formatDisplayDate` / `formatDisplayDateTime` from `src/utils/date-display.ts` (`05 Jul 2026` format).
- HTTP: `apiGet` / `apiPost` / `apiPatch` / `apiDelete`; `Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>`.
- Tokens in `src/utils/key-chain-storage/` only — never plain AsyncStorage for auth.

## Before finishing

Run `npm run verify:all` (or scoped verify) when touching app code.

## Parity

Foundational changes (http, auth, storage, types, toast) must land in **both** apps in the same change set unless explicitly scoped.
